quran[11{c,v,t}:
39,57,"ya kahe"" kash Allah ne mujhe hadaayat bakhsh hoti to mein bhi Muttaqiyun mein se hota """
39,58,"ya azaab dekh kar kahe"" kash mujhe aik mauqa aur mil jaye aur mein bhi naik amal karne walon mein shaamil ho jaoon """
39,59,"( aur uss waqt usay yeh jawab miley ke )"" kyun nahi, meri ayaat tairay paas aa chuki theen, phir to ne inhen jhtlaya aur taqqabur kya aur to kafiroon mein se tha """
39,60,aaj jin logon ne khuda par jhoot bandhay hain qayamat ke roz tum dekho ge ke un ke mun kalay hon ge kya jahannum mein mtkbron ke liye kaafi jagah nahi hai ?
39,61,"is ke bar aks jin logon ne yahan taqwa kya hai un ke asbaab kamyabi ki wajah se Allah un ko nijaat day ga, un ko nah koi gznd puhanche ga aur nah woh ghamgeen hon ge"
39,62,Allah har cheez ka khaaliq hai aur wohi har cheez par nigehbaan hai
39,63,zameen aur asmano ke khazanon ki knjyan usi ke paas hain aur jo log Allah ki ayaat se kufar karte hain wohi ghatay mein rehne walay hain
39,64,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho"" phir kya ae جاہلو, tum Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki bandagi karne ke liye mujh se kehte ho? """
39,65,( yeh baat tumhe un se saaf keh dainee chahiye kyunkay ) tumhari taraf aur tum se pehlay guzray hue tamam anbia ki taraf yeh wahi bhaije ja chuki hai ke agar tum ne shirk kya to tumhara amal zaya ho jaye ga aur tum khasaray mein raho ge
39,66,lehaza ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum bas Allah hi ki bandagi karo aur shukar guzaar bundon mein se ho jao
39,67,inn logon ne Allah ki qader hi nah ki jaissa ke is ki qader karne ka haq hai ( is ki qudrat kamila ka haal to yeh hai ke ) qayamat ke roz poori zameen uss ki muthi mein ho gi aur aasman is ke dast raast mein liptay hue hon ge pak aur balatar hai woh is shirk se jo yeh log karte hain
